<section id="section2">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">What can Quarry Bay School offer your family?</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="wrapper bg-colour2">
        <div class="container">
            <ul>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/19c606604184f5e978d044939bbd9460.png" alt="ESF_Logomark_BW_RGB" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">ESF Network</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>As part of the English Schools Foundation (ESF), our students are supported by the largest English-medium international school organisation in Hong Kong, providing them the resources and opportunities not found outside of ESF Schools.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://qbs.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/marketing_family/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/dfaf54533baa7729f2a2cbc2d81d133d.png" alt="World-class Education" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">World-class Education</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>At ESF schools, we provide a world-class education that is renowned for its academic excellence and rigorous curriculum. Our dedicated teachers and staff ensure that every student receives the best possible learning experience.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://qbs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/curriculum/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/9f8e7d1205e4cf7f44918ac11d9d0d80.png" alt="Comprehensive Student Support" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Comprehensive Student Support</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Our schools offer comprehensive support systems, including personalised guidance, pastoral care, and counselling services, to help students thrive academically, emotionally, and socially.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://qbs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/student_support_wellbeing/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/16e0c2b8b8d8e688933904666d02b278.png" alt="Strong School-Family Connection" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Strong School-Family Connection</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>We believe in fostering a strong partnership between schools and families. We actively encourage parental involvement and maintain open lines of communication to ensure that parents are fully engaged in their child's educational journey.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://qbs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/parent_partnership/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/7222b2dd0f4d682a4bc2a134ba455236.png" alt="Well-rounded Education" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Well-rounded Education</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Alongside academic excellence, our well-rounded education cultivates talents, interests, and character through diverse co-curricular activities in sports, arts, music, and community service.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://qbs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/our_approach/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/a9b58c8b652622bb740ad013be2b7f09.png" alt="Multicultural Environment" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Multicultural Environment</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Our schools embrace diversity and create a multicultural environment where students from different backgrounds come together to learn and grow. We celebrate cultural differences, promote inclusivity, and prepare students to thrive in a globalised world.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://qbs.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/what_we_stand_for/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(window).load(function() {
            $('h3', '#section2').each(function() {
                let img = $(this).parent().children('img');
                if(img.length) {
                    $(this).css('top', img.offset().top + img.height() + 25 - $(this).parent().offset().top);
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section3">
    <img src="/cache/img/bb3192b32072c698cf158816c67923f5.jpg" alt="IMG_3333" loading="lazy" width="1722" height="1294" />    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="section-title-container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="colour2">Primary Years Programme (PYP)</h2>
                <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tabs">
                            <button class="tab current" data-id="1">Years 1 - 6</button>
                    </div>
                            <div class="tab-content current" data-id="1">
                                <article class="editor"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As an IB World School, we're proud to offer the Primary Years Programme (PYP) - a transformative curriculum that nurtures the whole child. Through transdisciplinary learning, our students develop the knowledge, skills, and mindset to become globally-minded, principled contributors committed to shaping a better world.</span></p></article>
                                    <a href="https://qbs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/curriculum/">
                        <span>Find out more</span>
                    </a>
                            </div>
                <script type="text/javascript">
            $(document).ready(function() {
                $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();

                $('.tab', '#section3').click(function() {
                    $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section3').removeClass('current');
                    $(this).addClass('current');
                    $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).data('id') + ']', '#section3').addClass('current');
                    $('select', '#section3').val($(this).data('id')).selectbox('refresh');
                    $('.select .select-container div', '#section3').show();
                    $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();
                });

                $('.tab-select', '#section3').change(function() {
                    $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section3').removeClass('current');
                    $('.tab[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']').addClass('current');
                    $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section3').addClass('current');
                    $('.select .select-container div', '#section3').show();
                    $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();
                });
            });
        </script>
    </div>
</section>
<section id="section4" data-total="4">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="bg bg-colour4"></div>
        <div class="section-title-container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="colour2">Life at Quarry Bay School</h2>
                <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="record-slider">
            <div class="slider-container">
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/6e7d82c1b60d9b778091a2aef2ec2613.jpg" alt="IMG_4882" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>Diversity, Equity and Inclusion</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>At QBS, we cultivate an equitable, inclusive environment where every individual is valued and empowered to reach their full potential. As a leading international school, we are steadfastly committed to continuously improving our diversity, equity, and inclusion practices to shape compassionate global citizens.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://qbs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/student_support_wellbeing/">
                                    <span>Find out more</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
