                            <h3>
                                <span>Environment and  Sustainability</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>At QBS, sustainability is at the core of everything we do. We are committed to fostering a place where working and learning go hand-in-hand with environmental stewardship. Through the seamless integration of sustainable practices across our campus, we strive to lead by example and cultivate environmental awareness within our wider community.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://qbs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/outdoor_learning">
                                    <span>Find out more</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
