                    <div class="post" data-id="127">
                        <time>05/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>QBS is transforming as we get ready for the PTA Centenary Fair tomorrow! We are buzzing with excitement to celebrate 100 years of community, history, and fun. <br><br>A massive shout-out to our incredible PTA and parent volunteers who have been working tirelessly behind the scenes to make this magic happen. <br><br>See you all tomorrow—let’s make history together!<br><br>#esfqbs #centenialfair #communityevent</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/d20dfdcdbaea04446e2da680251c7db1.jpg" alt="625896646_18107487526778564_1079919448185570595_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="126">
                        <time>29/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>QBS got a hands-on look at the vibrant world of Cantonese Opera today. <br>Our students learned how instruments and percussion set the heartbeat of the play, the symbolism behind accessories and costumes, and most importantly, they witnessed the immense rigour required to master the "four basic skills": singing, acting, delivery of spoken lines, and martial arts.<br>We now have a new appreciation for the hard work and heart that keep this beautiful tradition alive.<br><br>A huge thank you to One Table Two Chairs Charitable Foundation for sharing their passion and showing us that behind every graceful gesture lies years of dedicated practice!<br><br>#esfqbs #cantoneseopera #1table2chairs #learningthrougharts #culturalheritage</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/ebddc20c90718daee97a766d8fcbfb0d.jpg" alt="624686241_18106648972778564_7527765642478338137_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="125">
                        <time>22/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>QBS were thrilled to welcome UK-based artist Caroline Cleave today as our Artist in Residence. Caroline spent an inspiring session with our Year 5 students, guiding them in creating beautiful, individually unique koi carp. Her warmth and expertise were a hit with the students, who loved the opportunity to learn from such a talented professional.<br><br>This visit was extra special for our community, as Caroline is the sister of our own Principal. It was a privilege to have her share her artistic passion with us, and we are incredibly proud of the stunning work our students produced under her mentorship. <br><br>Thank you, Caroline!<br><br>#esfqbs #artistinresidence #learningthrougharts</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/cadf9fd870ea331f5975312f89194bb8.jpg" alt="619265003_18106002823778564_6086421426463481758_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="124">
                        <time>15/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>Big congrats to Karisse and Avery for winning the HKPSSA Table Tennis Championship today! The skill level, focus, and sportsmanship they displayed were truly impressive. A huge thank you to all the participants and volunteers who made the event run smoothly.<br>#esfqbs #hkpssatabletennischampionship #learningthroughsport #weareqbs</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/d235a7a734fc4d71bf0469f5738b8cde.jpg" alt="613492380_18105367420778564_3859264923145846269_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="123">
                        <time>09/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>This Saturday, 10 January, marks the official anniversary of our 1926 opening. <br>Today, we held a special birthday assembly, and all year groups participated in various activities and challenges based on the number 100. <br>Earlier in the week, students also collaborated to create a spectacular piece of aerial photography spelling out 'QBS 100.' <br><br>Happy Birthday, QBS! Stay tuned, as more celebration events will be announced soon.<br><br>#esfqbs #celebrating100years #happybirthdayQBS #weareqbs #qbs100</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/73f11d70abb18e7970e5c79746becf6a.jpg" alt="610740348_18104861113778564_8655851017989591434_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                    </div>
