                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>The annual Chinese New Year collaboration between Chinese International School (@cishk) and Quarry Bay School once again brought our two school communities together to welcome the Year of the Horse. This tradition featured a joint visual arts project sharing ongoing appreciation for how art unites us across borders and backgrounds. <br>The opening ceremony was a joyful occasion attended by students from both schools, along with Ms Gardon, Principal of Chinese International School, Mr Cogbill, Vice Principal of Quarry Bay School, and the visual arts teachers. <br><br>#esfqbs #cishk #artscollaboration #cny2026 #yearofthehorse</h3>
